overview: Today on Private, Candee Licious needs something more beautiful than words, she needs intimacy and passion, and alongside Janice Griffith, Sara Diamante and Tory Sweety, she’s about to get it! That’s right, there’s nothing quite like a romantic session of love making, and although we often like the explore the wild side of sex here on Private, sometimes our girls just like to get up close and personal and enjoy an intimate one on one! Private Specials, Intimacy & Passion Vol.2, are you ready?
title: Intimacy & Passion 2
